"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-olympic-boxes-podium-prize-medal-winners-revealed-21334659\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"With theOlympicsnow well into the first week,medals are being handed outfor the winning athletes ofParis2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But fans have noticed that during the medal presentation, athletes are also given a long gold box while they are on the podium.\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether they win gold, silver or bronze, Olympic medallists are traditionally given gifts during the victory ceremonies.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest updates on the 2024 Olympics  At Tokyo 2020, athletes received a small bouquet of yellow, green and blue flowers.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At Rio 2016, medallists were presented with a small model of the official logo.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile,London2012 also opted to give flowers to those on the podium.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 have opted to go for something completely different as inside the gold box is the Games' 'Iconic Poster', specially created for this summer's competition.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998074145, \"rank\": 1.9247277528907612e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 organisers called on Ugo Gattoni create the special 'Iconic Poster' for the Games.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998074145, \"rank\": 1.9247277528907612e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gattoni is renowned worldwide for his style which is marked by fantasy and surrealisms, and includes both huge and tiny details in his work.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris-born artist spent more than 2,000 hours across six months to produce the designs for the posters.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the prizes do not end there for the winning athletes as they are also presented with a 'medallist mascot' after the ceremony when they return to the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3941386327569336e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 collaborated with Doudou et Compagnie Group to design a specialmedallist version of the Phryges.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998074145, \"rank\": 1.9247277528907612e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold, silver and bronze colours are featured on the medal emblem which is sewn on the mascot's belly, on its shoes and on the letters spelling out 'Bravo' on the back.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 president, Tony Estanguet - an Olympic gold medalist in canoe slalom, said of the mascots: 'We chose an ideal rather than an animal.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998074145, \"rank\": 1.9247277528907612e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canoe_slalom\", \"score\": 0.9491363252310581, \"rank\": 0.05358943011322514, \"text\": \"slalom\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canoe_slalom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canoe_slalom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We chose the Phrygian cap because it's a very strong symbol for the French Republic.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phrygian cap\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\", \"score\": 0.6512476436600418, \"rank\": 0.5352794179915363, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For French people, it's a very well-known object that is a symbol of freedom.'\", \"from\": 18